    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 36-39.</p><p>Burst of Divinity</p><p>Also at 20th level, as an action, you can expend 1 Legendary Point and point your holy symbol at a creature you can see within 60 feet. You either restore hit points to the creature equal to your level x 5 or have the creature take an amount of Necrotic or Radiant damage (your choice) equal to your level x 5.</p></div>",
